Name: Kāṣirtu
ind.Name: Kāṣirtu
Biography: Her father is Bēl-rēmanni, son of Nabû-zēru-ukīn, descendant of the Ahhēa family.

Name: Marduk-šumu-ibni
ind.Name: Marduk-šumu-ibni
Biography: Protagonist of the Ilia A+B archive. Younger brother of Nabû-bēlšunu and older brother of Nabû-ēṭer-napšāti and Nergal-iddin. Husband of {{f}}Inṣabtu/Marduk-šumu-iddin//Ša-nāšišu. Father of Nabû-balassu-iqbi (Nabû-bullissu), {{f}}Amat-Nanāya, {{f}}Amat-Ninlil and {{f}}Binunu. Grandfather of Libluṭ/Nabû-balāssu-iqbi.

Name: Nabû-mukīn-apli
ind.Name: Nabû-mukīn-apli
Biography: His family name should probably be Uballissu-Gula. It is likely that the scribe of BM 30958 made a mistake of writing his family name as Uballissu-Marduk because the preceding witness had that family name.

Name: Nabû-šākin-šulmi
ind.Name: Nabû-šākin-šulmi
Biography: The family name Ir’anni often occurs in its variant form Rē’ānu in Borsippa.
